    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) with your <strong>mayo</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>salad dressing</strong></p>",
