      "instruction": "<p>Spread the <strong>garlic mayo </strong>over the <strong>warmed brioche base</strong>, then pile up the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> and<strong> crispy fried hake</strong>, topping with the <strong>warmed brioche lid</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> fries</strong>,<strong> diced tomato</strong> and any <strong>remaining shredded lettuce </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>salad dressing </strong>over the<strong> </strong>tomato and lettuce</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
